{"type": "article", "id": 40594, "title": "Coach 买了 Kate Spade，以及，Banksy 创作“脱欧”壁画 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-05-09T02:39:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1922, "name": "Celine"}, {"id": 2097, "name": "USB"}, {"id": 18579, "name": "OFF-WHITE"}, {"id": 40235, "name": "功能手机"}, {"id": 40236, "name": "宠物衣服"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 138, "name": "Banksy"}, {"id": 7113, "name": "Kanye West"}, {"id": 10366, "name": "Kim Kardashian"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170509103906180QzjkUMLaRFJNq.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/coach-inks-2-4b-cash-deal-kate-spade-co-mergers-acquisitions-handbags-10883104/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>24 亿美元，Coach 正式收购 Kate Spade</strong></a> | 昨日，Coach 宣布已就收购 Kate Spade 签署正式协议。根据交易条款，Kate Spade 股东将获得每股 18.5 美元现金，总收购金额为 24 亿美元，Coach 集团将以银行定期贷款与 12 亿美元的现金支付相关款项。消息传出后，Kate Spade 股价大涨 8.5% 至每股 18.41 美元，Coach 集团股价则上涨了 7.8% 至每股 45.79 美元，目前市值约为 128 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/hennes-mauritz-group-sales-climb-7-april-10883078/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 集团四月销售额上涨 7%</strong></a> | H&amp;M 集团四月销售数据显示，销售额同比上涨 7%，目前集团在全球共有 4474 家门店，H&amp;M 将于 6 月 29 日公布上半年财报数据。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>神秘的涂鸦艺术家 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/banksy-mural-european-union-flag\" rel=\"nofollow\">Banksy，日前在英国东南部港口 Dover 创作了最新壁画</a>。Banksy 以欧盟旗帜为主体，描绘了一位工作人员爬上梯子，将其中一颗代表英国的星星“拆除”的场景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509094930Uj2qGHni8hJTCIF0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上个周末，纽约宠物用品品牌 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/03/23/puppy-streetwear-pawkier/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pawkier</a> 在纽约第十一大道和第十二大道之间开了一个为期一天的<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/06/pawkier-dog-streetwear-pop-up-shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">快闪店</a>。店内售出了专门为狗狗打造的“潮牌”衣物，包括 VLONE、YEEZY、Anti Social Social Club、OFF-WHITE 等潮牌的同款。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095018oy7YOavxubUR9nAG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095018dvcmaZBuHKz9ip0W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095018nBY90RVOW2s6ejq8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095019x3OhiTws6PUcaKWd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095019HmSauKPVs4BOnxzI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095019wcKYD7BIN4JhPfSz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090950271VegdSyl3tGBTw2h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095018Lm51HTF4GRa8lP3u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090950198bj56qTXEzVmgYNO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Off-White 最近与德国 USB 品牌 USBéton 合作，推出了一款水泥外壳、极具工业感的 USB。这款<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/off-white-x-usbeton-usb\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Off-White x USBéton </a>有 16GB 的储存空间，定价为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095108IT0cUAgB3boqswmd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/kim-kardashian-kanye-west-launch-thekidssupply\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Kim Kardashian 与 Kanye West 共同打造的全新童装直线 TheKidsSupply 已正式登陆官网</a>。<a href=\"https://thekidssupply.com\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">TheKidsSupply </a>有点像是缩小版的 YEEZY Season，包括迷彩印花连帽衫、运动裤、圆领卫衣、帽子，以及女生的蕾丝裙和 choker 等，定价从 22 至 240 美元不等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095242of6eU0JCxuSqEz8Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095242SkY9XFhGKfIuPOJ0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095243vqtH1yozkJsTZVI9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050909524243pTAUz76ZfB2qKy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095243FXcBPDWsQhEw2jo5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095243ZN7a2mHy5hDSgjIM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095243ZrYAlHM20Q63DcSd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095244gMv5ZEUhzXsxILOG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090952449nh8ovD61pV40Sy5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095245Ll5PXtuWIamgHw1D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095245dFR8UCcTaueoji2N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090952465lsovuak26e3B1hj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095248XeLchFGs7jTkMVPw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095306reGSIYhFjDp9wMbT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095306k3bM5WJAxzwqtvec.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095306WPsux6KRGUBp4ECz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095307r4LnOYZs3HykdGcW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095307gf7NabVEyDsTHcSO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090953073T4zbdWvxN0RGEJs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/celine-soft-cube-handbag/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Céline 2017 秋季系列推出全新袋款 Soft Cube</a>。该系列包袋有着立方体的形状，弧形的边角和柔软的材质，包括黑色、红色、姜黄色、咖啡色，以及秋冬专属的毛皮款。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095335IHLfBgslQ5TvScJ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090953359qycKwhedOMDHlLb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095335pShaOTjxGFIAKHVr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095341tINTGcJSi7PpoLmk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095341kHGKYqbi3RrgeXE5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/08/prada-resort-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 2018 度假系列发布</a>。这是 Prada 首次为早春系列独立办秀，秀场选在了米兰最早的购物中心 Vittorio Emanuele II。该系列以运动休闲为主题，辅以淡色薄纱、羽毛坠饰、亮片刺绣和金属光泽的配饰装点，少女感十足。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095445eAPWidR47ljyVSMO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095445jIHqSRv0U8ZGdQoV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095458pSDixuoP6Xy49GMH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095446c9Cx5ESYjMI6bWtL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095448wPUOqoAgHshujDJV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095451FLax4K3hmkXNyZjo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095445SxglHGJaMjWrPN7b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090954548JaQYEg6vc20iASf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095457pzJ6gPEQ4evXbhSW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095454duo7fVRsphxAN6OC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095455Dpz8s6G1hFAXJ3EU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201705090954557oTtcyaWmbUpAVjC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509095457Xp45flSiN2HjVPyk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/05/07/the-minimal-light-phone/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a>、<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/5/banksy-mural-european-union-flag\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}